        "prerequisite": "*Familiar Sage Dedication*",
        "requirement": "You aren't encumbered.",
        "frequency": "once per 10 minutes",
        "effect": "(air) Your familiar summons winds that speed up and protect you. You gain a +10-foot status bonus to your Speed until the end of your turn. When you Stride this turn, you don\u2019t trigger reactions. In addition, you don\u2019t need to Stride before a Long Jump this turn.",
